pkdnn.export.exportsd.save_state_dict(sd, stream)[source]

Saves a PyToch state dictionary using the format that TorchSharp can read.

Parameters:

  • sd – A dictionary produced by ‘model.state_dict()’

  • stream – An write stream opened for binary I/O.

Loads a PyTorch state dictionary using the format that saved by TorchSharp.

A dictionary can be loaded by ‘model.load_state_dict()’
